### ViettelPost Webhook + BullMQ Testing
### Use REST Client extension in VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@webhookToken = your-webhook-token-here
@adminToken = your-admin-jwt-token-here
@userToken = your-user-jwt-token-here

### 1. Test Webhook - Order Delivered (Status 501)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/viettelpost
Content-Type: application/json
X-ViettelPost-Token: {{webhookToken}}

{
  "ORDER_NUMBER": "VTP123456789",
  "ORDER_STATUS": 501,
  "ORDER_STATUS_NAME": "Đã giao hàng",
  "PRODUCT_NAME": "Áo thun nam",
  "RECEIVER_NAME": "Nguyễn Văn A",
  "RECEIVER_PHONE": "0901234567",
  "RECEIVER_ADDRESS": "123 Đường ABC, Quận 1, TP.HCM",
  "MONEY_COLLECTION": 500000,
  "MONEY_TOTAL": 500000,
  "UPDATE_DATE": "2024-01-15 10:30:00"
}

### 2. Test Webhook - Order Returned (Status 502)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/viettelpost
Content-Type: application/json
X-ViettelPost-Token: {{webhookToken}}

{
  "ORDER_NUMBER": "VTP987654321",
  "ORDER_STATUS": 502,
  "ORDER_STATUS_NAME": "Hoàn trả",
  "UPDATE_DATE": "2024-01-15 11:00:00"
}

### 3. Test Webhook - Order Cancelled (Status 504)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/viettelpost
Content-Type: application/json
X-ViettelPost-Token: {{webhookToken}}

{
  "ORDER_NUMBER": "VTP111222333",
  "ORDER_STATUS": 504,
  "ORDER_STATUS_NAME": "Đã hủy",
  "UPDATE_DATE": "2024-01-15 12:00:00"
}

### 4. Claim QR Voucher (User)
POST {{baseUrl}}/vouchers/claim-qr
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "orderCode": "VTP123456789",
  "voucherId": "your-voucher-uuid-here"
}

### 5. Get My Vouchers (User)
GET {{baseUrl}}/vouchers/user/my-vouchers
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 6. Get All Vouchers (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/vouchers

### 7. Get Voucher by ID (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/vouchers/your-voucher-uuid-here

### 8. Manual Trigger Verification (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/vouchers/manual-verify
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9. Bull Board Dashboard
# Open in browser: http://localhost:3001/admin/queues

### 10. Test Invalid Webhook Token (Should return 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/viettelpost
Content-Type: application/json
X-ViettelPost-Token: invalid-token

{
  "ORDER_NUMBER": "TEST123",
  "ORDER_STATUS": 501
}

### 11. Test Webhook with Missing Token (Should return 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/viettelpost
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ORDER_NUMBER": "TEST123",
  "ORDER_STATUS": 501
}

### Notes:
# - Replace {{webhookToken}} with actual token from ViettelPost
# - Replace {{adminToken}} with JWT token from admin login
# - Replace {{userToken}} with JWT token from user login
# - Replace voucher UUIDs with actual IDs from your database
# - Use ngrok for testing with real ViettelPost webhooks:
#   ngrok http 3001
#   Then register: https://your-ngrok-url.ngrok.io/webhooks/viettelpost
